snippet.title: Let's Play The Super Effective Turnabout! [BLIND] Gotta Press 'Em All!
snippet.description:
So ropfa made a little PW/Pokemon crossover and it's really charming...

(Also I found out PyWright can do this! But you can see when I figured this out in another time, another place, another Road... to... another Turnabout?)
